Another lesson comes from the response

00:17:52.410 --> 00:17:54.410
of Jonathan's armor bearer

00:17:54.410 --> 00:17:57.410
at 1 Samuel 147.

00:17:57.410 --> 00:18:00.410
At this, his armor bearer said to him,

00:18:00.410 --> 00:18:03.410
do whatever your heart impelled you to do,

00:18:03.410 --> 00:18:05.410
turn wherever you wish,

00:18:05.410 --> 00:18:09.410
and I will follow you wherever your heart impelled you.

00:18:09.410 --> 00:18:11.410
It is unlikely that the attendant

00:18:11.410 --> 00:18:15.410
would have initiated this challenging mission on his own.

00:18:15.410 --> 00:18:17.410
Jonathan's confident lead

00:18:17.410 --> 00:18:20.410
was a positive motivating influence on the man.

00:18:20.410 --> 00:18:23.690
What happens today when elders

00:18:23.690 --> 00:18:25.690
and overseers take the lead

00:18:25.690 --> 00:18:29.690
and display zeal in Jehovah's work like Jonathan?

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:31.690
Others in the congregation

00:18:31.690 --> 00:18:33.690
are also motivated to action

00:18:33.690 --> 00:18:35.690
while they are fine example.

