He sought Jehovah's direction

00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:32.410
by means of a sign,

00:19:32.410 --> 00:19:35.410
what a powerful reminder for us.

00:19:35.410 --> 00:19:38.410
Regardless of any natural abilities,

00:19:38.410 --> 00:19:41.410
acquired skills, or experience we may have,

00:19:41.410 --> 00:19:43.410
the key to success

00:19:43.410 --> 00:19:46.410
is seeking Jehovah's guidance and support.

00:19:46.410 --> 00:19:48.410
We seek His direction

00:19:48.410 --> 00:19:50.410
through specific prayers,

00:19:50.410 --> 00:19:53.410
Bible reading, and meditation,

00:19:53.410 --> 00:19:57.410
and applying direction from the faithful and discreet slave.

00:19:57.410 --> 00:20:01.410
We also consult with long-time faithful brothers and sisters

00:20:01.410 --> 00:20:03.410
who can share their rich experience

00:20:03.410 --> 00:20:05.410
as God's fellow workers.

00:20:05.410 --> 00:20:10.849
One such example was sister Joy Oram,

00:20:10.849 --> 00:20:14.849
who served in the Britain ranch.

00:20:14.849 --> 00:20:16.849
She shared her experiences

00:20:16.849 --> 00:20:18.849
in an archived interview

00:20:18.849 --> 00:20:23.849
sometime before finishing her earthly course in 2011.

00:20:23.849 --> 00:20:25.849
Listen also to the comments

00:20:25.849 --> 00:20:27.849
of her fellow workers in Britain

00:20:27.849 --> 00:20:35.940
who benefited from their time together.

