they struck down about 20 men.

00:27:29.380 --> 00:27:32.380
Even after receiving a clear sign from Jehovah,

00:27:32.380 --> 00:27:35.380
it took great effort.

00:27:35.380 --> 00:27:38.380
They had to climb up on their hands and feet,

00:27:38.380 --> 00:27:43.380
exerting themselves vigorously over rugged terrain.

00:27:43.380 --> 00:27:45.380
The lesson?

00:27:45.380 --> 00:27:47.380
Even when we received clear direction,

00:27:47.380 --> 00:27:49.380
and are ready to obey,

00:27:49.380 --> 00:27:53.380
carrying out our assignments will not always be easy.

00:27:53.380 --> 00:27:56.380
We have to exert ourselves vigorously,

00:27:56.380 --> 00:28:01.380
being willing to work hard with all of our mind, heart, and strength.

00:28:01.380 --> 00:28:07.819
How did the Philistines react to seeing Jehovah's support for his people?

