00:28:29.819 --> 00:28:33.819
Soon the Israelites, even those who had previously fled in fear,

00:28:33.819 --> 00:28:37.819
joined the victory battle over the Philistines.

00:28:37.819 --> 00:28:41.819
Likewise, when we put our hearts into theocratic assignments,

00:28:41.819 --> 00:28:45.819
Jehovah, our best fellow worker,

00:28:45.819 --> 00:28:51.819
will always come through with whatever we need to accomplish his will.

